Eric Hunting:

"This project by Richard Nelson's includes both an open source solar roof hydroponics farming system (an NFT type hydroponic farm built into a roofing system) and the dynamic liquid insulation technology (soap foam as active solar collection/insulation) it uses and can be used in other greenhouse structures. Currently developing prototype architecture in Malaysia."


